  <title>Zoom to Magnify a Specified Rectangular Area</title>
  <shortdesc>You can specify a rectangular area defined
 by two corners to display
 the objects within
 that area as large as possible.</shortdesc>
  <taskbody>
    <context>
      <p>
        <table>
