 The lower-left corner of the specified area becomes the lower-left corner of the new view.</p>
      <p>Zoom in using Window</p>
      <p>
        <table>
          <tgroup cols="1" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
            <colspec colname="c1" align="left" />
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry colname="c1">
