                  </fig>
                </entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </table>
 To zoom into an area using a window</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Choose View &gt; Zoom &gt; Window
 from the main menu.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select one corner of the window
 aroundthe area you want to magnify.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Specify the opposite corner
 of the window around the area youwant to magnify.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
